title: What happened to my game
body:
I did a game earlier as Annie mid,
I won only to be surprised
To see my game had become a place meant instead one of my promotion victories in towards Bronze 1.
But after the next game my promotion series was back,

What happened???!!

replies.body: There is a difference between the ranked flex que and the ranked solo/duo que. But, you might of been in the same que IDK I can't check.
I did ranked solo/duo for both
